title: SonicWall: VPN Security Associations
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/sonicwall
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the active VPN security associations (SAs) of
 SonicWall firewalls. For each SA the encrypted and decrypted throughput
 is reported as a rate.

 The check is always OK as long as the SA is present in the device data.

 The check uses the SONICWALL-FIREWALL-IP-STATISTICS-MIB.

item:
 The name of the VPN security association.

discovery:
 One service is created for each VPN security association.
